sub_interface_acls.102-acl:
ip access-list extended 102
 10 remark Allow ICMP
 10 permit icmp any any
 20 remark Remote Store Subnets
 20 deny   ip any 10.160.0.0 0.7.255.255
 30 deny   ip any 10.93.0.0 0.0.255.255
 40 deny   ip any 10.94.0.0 0.0.255.255
 50 deny   ip any 10.95.0.0 0.0.255.255
 60 deny   ip any 10.96.0.0 0.0.255.255
 70 permit ip any any
sub_interface_acls.121-acl:
ip access-list extended 121
 10 remark Allow ICMP
 10 permit icmp any any
 20 remark Allow Local 120 and 130 Subnets
 20 permit ip 10.161.0.0 0.0.0.31 10.162.0.0 0.0.0.31
 30 permit ip 10.162.0.0 0.0.0.31 10.161.0.0 0.0.0.31
 40 remark Remote Store Subnets
 40 deny   ip any 10.160.0.0 0.7.255.255
 50 deny   ip any 10.93.0.0 0.0.255.255
 60 deny   ip any 10.94.0.0 0.0.255.255
 70 deny   ip any 10.95.0.0 0.0.255.255
 80 deny   ip any 10.96.0.0 0.0.255.255
 90 permit ip any any
141: remark Store to Store Voip Calls
sub_interface_acls.141-acl:
ip access-list extended 141
 10 remark Allow ICMP
 10 permit icmp any any
 20 remark Store to Store Voip Calls
 20 permit udp any 10.163.0.0 0.0.255.255 range 16384 32767
 30 remark Remote Store Subnets
 30 deny   ip any 10.160.0.0 0.7.255.255
 40 deny   ip any 10.93.0.0 0.0.255.255
 50 deny   ip any 10.94.0.0 0.0.255.255
 60 deny   ip any 10.95.0.0 0.0.255.255
 70 deny   ip any 10.96.0.0 0.0.255.255
 80 permit ip any any
